SUMMARY:Part Closure: BAKERLOO LINE: Saturday 16 and Sunday 17 August\, no 
 service between Queens Park and Harrow & Wealdstone. There will also be no
  LIONESS LINE service between Euston and Watford Junction. LONDON NORTH 
 WESTERN RAILWAY services will serve Harrow & Wealdstone\, on both days. 
 Special bus services operate.
